heyy...well today is finally friday!! Oh mn the Green Day concert last night was AMAZING!!!!!!!!!!  Fisrt we got there a little too bit early lol...but once we got inside lisa and jackie got through but my ticket wouldn't Scan right...................................So this big secruity guy said too me "Will You Please Come With Me"  O mann i got so scared i thought he was ganna kick me out or something......but he just went to the box office too make sure it wasn't a fake and obvilously it wasn't so he gave me my wrist band and i went in. and cought back up with jackie and lisa.  We got to the floor and we got right up at the fecnce in the front.  Sugarcult satrted and it was so cool cuz we were so close to them...but that only lasted two songs....b/c i was right up agianst the railing.....and i was getting smushed and i could barley breath lol so jackie was behind me trying to not have people kill me...so after the second song we just backed up a little bit.  Then NFG came on after them and it was our 3 time seeing them, their intro was awsome...but not nearly as good as Green Day!  NFG finseshd and then we got some drinks and came back to the pit for Green Day.  Oh mann they came on and it was SOOO GOOD!!!! i can't believe how good green day is in concert they keep the crowd entertained adn everything... iT was funny when the lead signer billy joe was felling himsefl up haha and then we sung "we are the champions" cuz we had won the wrold series!  They played basket case (of coarse) and they started with American Idiot.  ( haha lisa 'Do the papiganda")  And then ended with Minority.   It is hands down the best show i have been to....
